Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.30,0:24:00.18,Default,,0,0,20,,to give me that loving glance once again
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.18,0:24:05.68,Default,,0,0,20,,Ah, how frustrating it is \Nto have these unrequited feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.68,0:24:10.64,Default,,0,0,20,,How are you feeling? I am Benio
