Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.00,0:01:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A new era begins. Our High Collar Lady\Nis determined to fight for freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.73,0:01:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and while on a mission to subvert \Nthis old mansion's way of life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.71,0:01:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,she encountered firm defense, and a resolute enemy\Ncommander who kept giving her test after test.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally, this drove Benio up the wall after\NShinobu's kindness granted Benio her first palpitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.71,0:01:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, the formidable enemy\Nirked her where she least expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.09,0:01:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Refusing to put up with it any longer,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.26,0:01:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,she now faces him in a life-or-death situation,\Nusing her tomboyish two-handed fencing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:03.70,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\c&HFAE7EB&\bord0\blur1.026\fs60\b1\pos(709,182)}Episode 10\N{\fs80}Gulp Down the Medicine of Love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.38,0:02:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my! He doesn't appear to be in a good spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.10,0:03:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How did this little girl do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.71,0:03:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She eluded my attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I have a real spear here against\Nher three-pronged stick. I simply can't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.97,0:03:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't go on easy her for being a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.56,0:03:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll skewer her all the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.89,0:03:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If a thrust lands... I might actually die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.99,0:04:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Just 10 more centimeters \Nand my life would have been no more...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.12,0:04:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.41,0:04:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you be a little more gentle, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.34,0:04:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't apply the patches\Nbecause you move too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stay still for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.93,0:04:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:05:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice to take care of you once in a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, for goodness' sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting defeated by the young girl like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.71,0:05:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Although, her swordsmanship \Nkind of reminded me of something...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.55,0:05:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.69,0:05:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That goes back a long, long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu's father, Soichirou, was still a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.19,0:05:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well done! You're strong, Soichirou!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.84,0:05:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And thirty years after that,\Nhe abandoned Shinobu and went abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.69,0:05:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Only to never come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That look on Benio...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same as Soichirou's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.91,0:05:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl's really something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, quiet! Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, I want to be left alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, you're flustered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.54,0:06:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Outta my way, go-go-go-go-go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.29,0:06:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey-hey, make way, make way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't blame me if you get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ranmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here, Ranmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.21,0:06:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.79,0:06:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy really is a weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.83,0:06:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right? He always goes crazy\Nif the neighboring girl's involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, Nanny, big news, big news, big news!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.61,0:06:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ushi, you look enthusiastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find a 200 yen coin?{二銭銅貨でも拾ったのか - this should be the sentence - must be because there are no 200 yen coins anymore / otherwise, just put something such as "Did something good happen?" if you want to remove specific references}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Even better! You think I'd be this\Nhappy from just finding some coins? {if I didn't mishear, he's saying 恵比寿, the God of fishing and commerce - alternatively, just remove the specific references}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.49,0:06:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Did anything happen to Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ranmaru! Perceptive as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:07:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to Lady Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanny, you need to prepare a grand meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Eek!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.41,0:07:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ushi, tell me the good news!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.83,0:07:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,After many things happened,\Nthe Boss will soon come back home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?! I didn't expect it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.21,0:07:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She hit that stubborn geezer with her stick\Nand she floored him! You should've seen it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.64,0:07:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray, Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.47,0:07:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That means Lady Benio\Nwill surely be booted from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.21,0:07:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, to cap it all!{あたりきしゃりきかっぱのへ - if you have better ideas put them, I wanted to keep the kappa joke}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.15,0:07:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Did someone call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.38,0:07:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, we need to\Ngive her a warm welcome soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Show her how happy we are to have her back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.17,0:07:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true! Bring out the red rice \Nto celebrate this occasion, Nanny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How foolish of her to break such\Na great engagement. What a waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so frustrated!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.64,0:08:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.99,0:08:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I need to tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.06,0:08:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.88,0:08:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So... How is the Count doing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so that's what this is about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.13,0:08:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.89,0:08:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry for acting recklessly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.89,0:08:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that big of a deal. He's been\Ntempering himself ever since he was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So please, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.06,0:08:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than that, Benio, \Nwhat is it you have there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.81,0:08:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, after I did such a thing to the Count...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.41,0:09:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My, Benio, don't be so worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.78,0:09:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything, he was greatly pleased by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.92,0:09:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Greatly pleased?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.93,0:09:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He likes strong-arm tactics.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.92,0:09:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear that's way better\Nfor him than simple medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.59,0:09:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,True, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,However, due to his stubbornness, he'll never openly admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, you're part of\Nour family. Don't forget that, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.61,0:09:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back to your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What? What's wrong with my heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's been wrong\Nwith it as of late, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.79,0:09:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Or so I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.21,0:10:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you again, missy. What an eyesore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My heartbeat's completely different now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.74,0:10:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be going, Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.68,0:10:34.41,Sign,,0,0,0,,Boss Benio's Greeting Party{/going to greet ...}{...お出迎えへ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Lady Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.47,0:10:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I have to fight her, too?{not sure, but I hear 戦闘開始}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.81,0:10:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this for the next schedule?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that.\NThere's a guest here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:10:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? To see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.97,0:10:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.42,0:11:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who it could be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.27,0:11:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.36,0:11:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! It's me!\NYou two never change, sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.29,0:11:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But you don't have to worry anymore.\NI won't return to this house ever again, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so it was you, Ushigorou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.34,0:11:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye. It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.64,0:11:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So what are you waiting for? \NIf you need something, come inside and find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,These two damn dogs won't let me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.56,0:11:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I understand, I said too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.42,0:11:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenmaru, Chimaru, \Nthis man is my dear henchman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you met him before?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.47,0:11:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, how'd you ever\Nmanage to tame them, Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.26,0:11:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything. \NThey just gradually warmed up to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.99,0:12:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's hurry you home before\Nyou win over any more animals in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I came to pick you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.26,0:12:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.00,0:12:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, hop in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.40,0:12:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You must know Nanny made grilled chicken, and even\NRanmaru put his heart into making roasted potatoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.35,0:12:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not coming home, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But you hit that old man on the head!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that made him like me more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But they still won't kick me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, even that stubborn\Ngeezer got won over by the Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.24,0:12:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, they'll all become her henchmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Like hell! This isn't real! \NI'm the only henchman she'll ever need!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.99,0:12:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's go home, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.51,0:12:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but my mission isn't complete yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.22,0:12:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Leveling this mansion's way of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.18,0:12:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one hell of an idea! I'll also join!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll always be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,by your side...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:12:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, scratch that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So, are you sure won't come home?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.85,0:13:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.99,0:13:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Grilled chicken and many\Ndelicious things are waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm weak to food, I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.93,0:13:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to eat them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.64,0:13:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.09,0:13:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll have to abstain for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.54,0:13:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou, you go eat the chicken\Nmeatballs and potatoes in my stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying that\NI'll have to meet these dudes again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.05,0:13:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.99,0:13:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu, oh you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.29,0:13:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she really the only\Nwoman appealing to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.34,0:13:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose you\Ncould always have an affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.93,0:13:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Insulting me right to my face...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this what they call "greatly pleased," huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandfather...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, men from\Nthe Meiji era were admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.91,0:14:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Very, very admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Keeping multiple mistresses in his\Nhouse only made that man more adorned.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I add some milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.51,0:14:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing...?! You monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.85,0:14:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.57,0:14:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize on behalf of all Japanese women!{not sure}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.29,0:14:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandfather, times have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.69,0:14:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, you can leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.51,0:14:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How long have I been living here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:15:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd go away in\Na snap, but it's taking so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.69,0:15:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanny...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.43,0:15:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,When it rains for long, \Nyou always have a headache.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.61,0:15:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.11,0:15:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Benio!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can't get married\Nto another man! Come back!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I, too, want to come back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.36,0:15:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened? It's pretty noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.89,0:15:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio, sorry for the loud noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, don't mind me. Did anything happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.76,0:15:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.79,0:15:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of this rain,\Nthe Count's neuralgia is worsening,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and it doesn't look like\Nit's going to get better any time soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.27,0:15:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you call the doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! I tried,\Nbut unfortunately, he's away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Neuralgia, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.78,0:16:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My nanny went through it, too. \NThat's a tough condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'll excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.66,0:16:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any geraniums?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.99,0:16:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chinese medicine ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.59,0:16:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,swertias, chameleon plants,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.51,0:16:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,plantagos, aractylodes, ginseng,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.51,0:16:21.43,Sign,,0,0,0,,{Those are the same plants she is naming}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.17,0:16:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,red spider lilies, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.36,0:16:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, could you find\Nthem and bring them to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.48,0:16:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to make my medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.04,0:16:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura's special medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? It's so strong that it made those dogs\Nrun away with their tails between their legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.29,0:17:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever, it's not like I'll drink it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.57,0:17:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.99,0:17:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Count.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.47,0:17:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, nobody's allowed to come in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.03,0:17:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's medicine for your neuralgia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need it!
Comment: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:36.12,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(822,152)\fs40\frz356.5\c&H292413&\3c&HA8A081&\frx4\fry16}Shinobu{Ninja/Shinobu}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just seeing your face is painful enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away, go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But it works wonders for my nanny.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.46,0:17:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? W-What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Chinese herbal medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need such unscientific things!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.40,0:17:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife only buys\Nreliable medicines from Germany!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.10,0:17:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This works better on Japanese people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink it and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.61,0:17:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What is this stench?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes me dizzy, I don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.73,0:18:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What now? Getting cold feet already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who's getting cold feet here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.99,0:18:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a real man as you say,\Nthen this medicine is nothing special, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.37,0:18:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.12,0:18:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I... drank it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.51,0:18:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.83,0:18:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! What's this lizard-like thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.76,0:18:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a charred newt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.55,0:18:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very effective!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.93,0:18:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A newt...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.26,0:18:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A newt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.52,0:18:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Count, you're already asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.44,0:18:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're visiting him, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.07,0:18:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll look after him for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.91,0:18:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go rest, Lady Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.11,0:18:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll do it by myself.\NYou can go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.78,0:18:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, I could do it myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.85,0:18:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you awake, Count?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.47,0:19:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You were sitting here all night long?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.81,0:19:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like it got better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.22,0:19:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Count...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How shameful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The daughter of a\Nshogunal vassal healed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.85,0:19:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, Count...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:20:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be true, but it's from way before\Nthe Meiji Restoration, and it's the Taishō Era now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.25,0:20:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that much myself,\Nbut I still despise vassals as a whole!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.98,0:20:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, my wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.57,0:20:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? She did what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.96,0:20:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Before marrying me,\Nshe was in love with a vassal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.79,0:20:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Who should be my grandfather, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.69,0:20:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.87,0:20:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And even after she married me,\Nshe still won't forget him no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.81,0:20:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Count...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.85,0:20:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I was aware that I could never be\N quite as handsome, so I tried to bear with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.38,0:20:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But she'd always keep watching wistfully into\Nthe distance with that dreamy look in her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.47,0:20:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They say your first love \Nstays with you for the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, Dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hearing that from you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.10,0:20:45.52,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Eek!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.36,0:20:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.98,0:20:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You heard that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.13,0:20:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My, how shameful...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you really always think I was like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.95,0:20:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, it's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.99,0:20:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after we had a son and\NI was faithful to you for so many years...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.68,0:21:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How shameful. Shameful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.45,0:21:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My love for that man is but a\Nbeautiful memory of the bygone times.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.00,0:21:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I know I can't spend\Nmy whole life living in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.15,0:21:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since the day we became united, \NI've been living for you only.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.55,0:21:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Then, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But you just kept focusing on\Nyour work and treating me as a bother,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.32,0:21:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,even though I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,love you so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear, what do you think about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.45,0:21:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.04,0:21:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.79,0:21:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.18,0:21:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He's always loved her...\NThat's why he hates vassals so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.47,0:21:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a bad impression of him,\Nbut he's really a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.34,0:22:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I could find\Nsomeone who loved me that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.12,0:22:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be lovely. Lovely!{reference to the first episode}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.23,0:22:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Shinobu?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.93,0:22:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Unthinkable!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.56,0:22:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy would leave out the "love" in\Nmarrying someone and wouldn't make much of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.81,0:22:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So give him to me!{hooray, I finally understood that she meant okure as 贈れ}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.28,0:22:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaddya want?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.52,0:22:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't give you anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.48,0:22:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.35,0:22:19.46,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.05,0:22:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.74,0:22:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.57,0:22:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.58,0:22:27.49,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.49,0:22:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A lady's heart changes like wind in a storm,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.31,0:22:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's nothing wrong with a High Collar Lady pursuing true love in the Taishō Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.68,0:22:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But where is her bluebird?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.73,0:22:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,To officialize his engagement with this lassie,\NShinobu organizes an outdoor party.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.99,0:23:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But hold on. Our High Collar Lady doesn't know\N any high-class manners, and many troubles await!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.41,0:23:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of it, all of a sudden,\Na seductive maiden appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.59,0:23:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on {\i1}Here Comes the High Collar Lady{\i0}:\N"Welcome to the Party of Grief"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.45,0:23:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
